data.description: Welcome home! This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is designed for comfortable living. The kitchen has been updated with granite counters, a stone backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. Enjoy the practicality of soft-close cabinet doors and a pantry for all your essentials. Step into the backyard oasis, perfect for family gatherings. The yard backs up to a preserve and features a fully fenced space with a wood shed, storage shed, and a firepit for those chilly evenings. Inside, the vinyl plank flooring and tile make cleaning a breeze. All appliances, including the washer and dryer, are included for your convenience. The primary ensuite offers double vanity and a linen closet, making daily routines more manageable. Tucked away on a cul-de-sac, this home is all about creating a comfortable haven for you and your family! Come, make this home your own! NEW ROOF installed December 2023
